HEADWORD: Cloudless
<hw>Cloud"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Without a cloud; clear;
bright.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A <qex>cloudless</qex> winter sky.</q>
<rj><qau>Bankroft.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Cloud"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
